issues.body:
Web view showing the wrong position of cursor pointer on a text form field.
The web app is also built using flutter and that URL is used in web view.

## Code Snippets

### For web view
You can use any one of packages [webview_flutter](https://pub.dev/packages/webview_flutter) OR [flutter_inappwebview](https://pub.dev/packages/flutter_inappwebview)

```dart
InAppWebView(
  initialUrlRequest: URLRequest(url: Uri.parse('flutter web app url')),
),
```
### Flutter web app
`main.dart`
I used the custom font `Open Sans`. downloaded `.ttf` files from [Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com/)

```dart
MaterialApp(
/// other code
theme: ThemeData(
  fontFamily: 'OpenSans'
)
```

`login_page.dart`
```dart
class LoginPage extends StatefulWidget {
  const LoginPage({Key? key}) : super(key: key);

  @override
  State<LoginPage> createState() => _LoginPageState();
}

class _LoginPageState extends State<LoginPage> {
  final _emailCtrl = TextEditingController();
  final _passwordCtrl = TextEditingController();

